---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FraiseQL Claims Verification - Proof & Evidence"
  description="Every performance metric and feature claim linked to source code, benchmarks, and working examples."
>
  <div style="padding: 2rem; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1>📋 Claims Verification Registry</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #666;">
      <strong>Every claim backed by proof: code, tests, benchmarks, or working examples</strong>
    </p>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>Performance Metrics (With Proof)</h2>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0;">
        <tr style="background: #f5f3ff;">
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Claim</th>
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Metric</th>
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Proof</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>fraiseql-wire</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Constant memory with streaming (vs buffered results)</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql-wire">Source</a> |
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql-wire/tree/main/benchmarks">Benchmarks</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background: #fafafa;">
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>pg_tviews</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Faster incremental view refresh (vs full rebuild)</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/pg_tviews">Source</a> |
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/pg_tviews/tree/main/benchmarks">Benchmarks</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>confiture</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">600× faster database builds</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/confiture">Source</a> |
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/confiture/tree/main/benchmarks">Benchmarks</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background: #fafafa;">
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>fraiseql-seed</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Faster test data generation with auto-resolution</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql-seed">Source</a> |
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql-seed/tree/main/benchmarks">Benchmarks</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>jsonb_delta</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Delta-based JSONB updates (reduced bandwidth)</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/jsonb_delta">Source</a> |
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/jsonb_delta/tree/main/benchmarks">Benchmarks</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background: #fafafa;">
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Ecosystem Combined</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Cumulative benefits when integrated together</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql-ecosystem">Analysis</a> |
            <a href="/ecosystem">Ecosystem Overview</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>Feature Claims (With Proof)</h2>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0;">
        <tr style="background: #f5f3ff;">
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Feature</th>
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Claim</th>
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Proof</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Compile-Time Optimization</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">All GraphQL interpretation at build time</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/crates/fraiseql-core/src/compiler">Compiler code</a> |
            <a href="/how-it-works">How It Works</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background: #fafafa;">
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>N+1 Prevention</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Compiler prevents N+1 query patterns</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/tests">Test suite</a> |
            <a href="/use-cases/n-plus-one">Example</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Multi-Database Support</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLite, SQL Server</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/crates/fraiseql-core/src/db">Database adapters</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background: #fafafa;">
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>100% Audit Trail</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">All mutations logged with cryptographic signatures</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/crates/fraiseql-core/src/audit">Audit code</a> |
            <a href="/for/compliance">Compliance guide</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Field-Level Encryption</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Automatic encryption for sensitive fields</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/crates/fraiseql-core/src/security">Security code</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background: #fafafa;">
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Apache Arrow Flight</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">25-40% compression vs JSON</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql-wire/tree/main/benchmarks">Benchmarks</a> |
            <a href="/for/data-engineers">Data Engineers Guide</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>RBAC at Compile Time</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Role-based access control verified by compiler</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/crates/fraiseql-core/src/auth">Auth code</a> |
            <a href="/use-cases/scattered-auth">Example</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>Test Coverage</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Total Tests:</strong> 2,400+ tests across all projects
          <br />
          <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/tests">Test suite</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Unit Tests:</strong> Per-module tests in Rust crates
          <br />
          <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/crates">Crate tests</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Integration Tests:</strong> End-to-end database tests
          <br />
          <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/tests/integration">Integration tests</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Performance Tests:</strong> Criterion benchmarks
          <br />
          <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/benchmarks">Performance tests</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>Examples as Proof</h2>
      <p>
        All 50+ examples in the FraiseQL repository are runnable, tested, and
        demonstrate specific features:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/examples">
            50+ Working Examples
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>Blog API (authentication, queries, mutations)</li>
        <li>E-Commerce API (complex relationships, inventory)</li>
        <li>Analytics Dashboard (Arrow Flight, materialized views)</li>
        <li>SaaS Platform (multi-tenant isolation, RBAC)</li>
        <li>Compliance Demo (audit logging, encryption)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>Code Quality Metrics</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Rust Safety:</strong> All <code>unsafe</code> blocks forbidden
          (clippy::forbid)
          <br />
          <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/blob/main/Cargo.toml">
            Cargo.toml config
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Linting:</strong> Clippy pedantic + deny on all targets
          <br />
          <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/blob/main/Cargo.toml">
            Clippy rules
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Type Safety:</strong> 100% type coverage (no implicit <code>Any</code>)
          <br />
          <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql/tree/main/crates">
            Crate types
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Documentation:</strong> All public items documented with examples
          <br />
          <a href="https://docs.rs/fraiseql-core/">
            API docs
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>Compliance & Security</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>HIPAA Ready:</strong> Audit logging, encryption, field-level access control
          <br />
          <a href="/for/compliance">Compliance guide</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>PCI-DSS Ready:</strong> Deterministic latency, encryption, audit trail
          <br />
          <a href="/use-cases/regulated-industries">Regulated industries example</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>SOC 2 Aligned:</strong> Security controls, availability, confidentiality
          <br />
          <a href="/for/compliance">Compliance setup</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>GDPR Compliant:</strong> Data deletion, encryption, consent management
          <br />
          <a href="/for/compliance">GDPR features</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>How to Verify Claims</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Clone the repo:</strong>
          <br />
          <code>git clone https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql</code>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Run tests:</strong>
          <br />
          <code>cargo test --all</code>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Run benchmarks:</strong>
          <br />
          <code>cargo bench</code>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Try examples:</strong>
          <br />
          <code>cd examples/blog_api && docker-compose up</code>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Check code:</strong>
          <br />
          All source available at{" "}
          <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql">
            github.com/fraiseql
          </a>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
